                  <interp inst="t18151025-47-crimeloc275" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18151025-47-off272 t18151025-47-crimeloc275"></join>. I sent a boy with half a tub of butter on the 10th of October, to Ratcliffe Highway. That butter was stolen; and in consequence of an information I received, I went to the prisoner's lodgings with an officer; we found some butter on the table there, which was mine.</p>
               <p>Cross examined Do you mean to say, that you will swear by the colour and the taste, that a bit of butter which was at the prisoner's lodgings, was part of the half rub of butter which somebody stole - A. Yes, I will swear it.</p>
               <p>
            
